Doc: The specification of whether the direction of a barrier within an FX OTC option is Down or Up.

Source.Contents:
/#
 The specification of whether the direction of a barrier within an FX OTC option is Down or Up.
 #/
enum FpML5.reporting.FxBarrierDirectionEnum {
    # The barrier is triggered if the observed rate is at or below the barrier level during the period of observation, or at the time of observation.
    Down 
    # The barrier is triggered if the observed rate is at or above the barrier level during the period of observation, or at the time of observation.
    Up 

}

Down.Doc: The barrier is triggered if the observed rate is at or below the barrier level during the period of observation, or at the time of observation.
Down.Name: Down

Up.Doc: The barrier is triggered if the observed rate is at or above the barrier level during the period of observation, or at the time of observation.
Up.Name: Up
